<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rancour" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rancour,</orth> malice, hatred: <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.308" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 308</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 143</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.144" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 144</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.2.89" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 3, 92</bibl>. <cit><quote>put --s in the vessel of my peace,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 1, 67</bibl></cit> (made myself live in discord with myself).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>